{"title":"Best Sellers","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"deep-sea-fish-oil-capsules-omega-3-2500-mg-lemon","title":"Deep Sea Fish Oil Capsules - 2500 mg Omega 3 (Lemon Flavored)","description":"\u003ch2\u003eNeuherbs Deep Sea Fish Oil – Omega-3 Capsules for Daily Wellness\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp align=\"justify\"\u003eLooking for the best fish oil capsules in India? neuherbs \u003cspan data-sheets-root=\"1\"\u003edeep sea fish oil\u003c\/span\u003e offers a triple-strength formula designed to support your overall health. These omega-3 fish oil capsules are lemon-flavoured to eliminate fishy burps, making them the perfect fish oil supplement for men and women alike.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eWhy Choose Neuherbs Fish Oil Capsules?\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp align=\"justify\"\u003eNeuherbs brings you premium-quality fish oil capsules sourced from small deep-sea fish like sardines and anchovies. Rich in EPA and DHA, these omega-3 fish oil capsules deliver 2500 mg of pure fish oil per serving and are added with Vitamins E and D3.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHeart Health:\u003c\/strong\u003e Promotes healthy cholesterol level and supports cardiac function.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eBrain Function:\u003c\/strong\u003e Improves memory, focus, \u0026amp; helps manage stress.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSkin \u0026amp; Hair:\u003c\/strong\u003e Among the best fish oil capsules for hair growth and glowing skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eWeight Management:\u003c\/strong\u003e Ideal fish oil capsules for weight loss and metabolism support.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eJoint \u0026amp; Bone Strength:\u003c\/strong\u003e Helps reduce inflammation and aids in muscle recovery.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eProduct Features\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTriple-Strength Omega-3 Fish Oil Capsuless (2500 mg per serving, 2 capsules)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e1486 mg of Omega-3s: 892 mg EPA + 594 mg DHA\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLemon-flavoured softgels – no fishy burps and aftertaste\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFortified with Vitamin D3 and E\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAvailable size includes fish oil 60 capsules and fish oil 200 capsules\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuitable for all: \u003cstrong\u003efish oil capsules for women\u003c\/strong\u003e improve hormone health and promote healthy pregnancy and fish oil capsules for men aid in post-workout muscle recovery, and brain and vision health.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eBest-Rated Fish Oil Supplements with Quality You Can Trust\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp align=\"justify\"\u003eOur original fish oil capsules undergo 10 quality checks, including molecular distillation and third-party testing to remove heavy metals like mercury, lead, and arsenic. Whether you're buying your first pack or switching to a cleaner brand, this is the best omega-3 fish oil capsule, acclaimed for purity, potency, and effectiveness.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eAffordable Fish Oil Capsules Price in India\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp align=\"justify\"\u003eWith neuherbs, you don’t just get the best omega-3 capsules, you get premium quality at a great value. Whether you are comparing fish oil capsules price or omega-3 capsules price, our range delivers unmatched benefits for the price.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eWho Should Use This?\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAnyone looking for omega-3 fish oil capsules for daily heart and brain health\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePeople seeking fish oil capsules for skin ageing or fish oil capsules for hair growth\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFitness enthusiasts using fish oil capsules for weight loss and recovery\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMen and women l