nction, and joint health. Combined with the True Vitamin Strength Booster, this combo delivers a potent dose of essential vitamins and minerals, ensuring optimal nutrient intake and supporting a strong immune system. \u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (60 Tablets + 60 Softgels)","offer_id":43368282226858,"sku":"NDSFO60NTV60","price":999.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/front_959785d0-6a5d-4a9f-929c-bef31f84e0a7.jpg?v=1729161581"},{"product_id":"skin-collagen-booster-hyaluronic-acid-glow","title":"Neuherbs Veg Collagen Powder with Antioxidants","description":"\u003cp\u003eneuherbs brought to you “Veg Collagen” with 5 Natural Antioxidants for healthy, glowing \u0026amp; firm skin. Made from “VegCol” a Veg Collagen Peptide Powder which is clinically tested veg collagen supplement for women \u0026amp; men who want youthful, glowing skin. Unlike ordinary collagen powder, neuherbs veg collagen powder for skin provides Triple-Action formula that replenishes, boosts \u0026amp; hydrates skin. It contains authentic veg collagen peptides that mimic Type 1 \u0026amp; 3 collagen to replenish lost collagen, help reduce wrinkles, and improve skin elasticity. In continuous use for 8 weeks, this collagen peptides powder has been shown to deliver visible results. Formulated with natural antioxidants, grape seed extract with 80% proanthocyanidins, citrus bioflavonoids, lycopene, ellagic acid, and 100% RDA of Vitamin C, it helps boost collagen production, protect skin from free-radical damage, repair \u0026amp; recover skin tissue damage and enhance skin texture. Added hyaluronic acid along with vegetarian collagen, locks in moisture to help keep skin supple, smooth \u0026amp; hydrated reducing dullness \u0026amp; dryness. \u003cbr\u003eWhether you’re looking for the best collagen supplements for women and men or effective skin supplements for glowing skin, neuherbs Veg Collagen – Collagen peptide powder offers a clean, vegan-friendly solution. With zero added sugar, no artificial preservatives, colours and maltodextrin, this collagen powder for women is easy to mix, tastes great in orange flavour, and makes skincare simple.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"1 Month Pack - (200 GM)","offer_id":41395537608874,"sku":"NSCB210MF","price":799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"2 Months Pack - (400 GM)=Recommended","offer_id":41395542294698,"sku":"NSCB210P2","price":1549.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/10.webp?v=1763965039"},{"product_id":"pure-himalayan-shilajit-resin-boost-stamina","title":"Pure Himalayan Shilajit Resin - Boost Stamina \u0026 Strength","description":"\u003cp style=\"text-align: justify;\" class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShilajit is a traditional Ayurvedic herb that has been used for centuries to help people with low stamina, endurance, and vitality. neuherbs shilajit resin is sourced from the high altitudes of the Himalayas for high potency \u0026amp; better results. neuherbs Pure Himalayan Shilajit Resin is purified using a Traditional Ayurvedic technique known as Suryataapi to retain its nutrients, benefits, and effectiveness. So, try neuherbs ’ Pure Himalayan Shilajit Resin and improve your strength, stamina \u0026amp; energy while reducing fatigue and getting your testosterone levels significantly higher. Since it is sourced from high ~18000 ft. altitudes, it offers you up to 75% of fulvic acid and the most potent form for optimal absorption and efficacy. neuherbs Pure Himalayan Shilajit is completely safe as it is tested for heavy metals from NABL.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Shilajit - (20 GM)","offer_id":44586359816362,"sku":"NPHS20","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Shilajit - (30 GM)=Recommended","offer_id":44363347951786,"sku":"NPHS30","price":999.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Pure_himalayan_shilajit_resin_1.webp?v=1769506439"},{"product_id":"gold-deep-sea-fish-oil-omega-3","title":"Gold Deep-Sea Fish Oil With Higher Strength Omega-3","description":"\u003cp\u003eLead a healthy, happy, and stress-free life knowing that you are continuously shielding your heart, brain, eye, and immunity with our uniquely formulated Omega-3 Gold Capsule.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eneuherbs Gold Deep-Sea Fish Oil Omega-3 Capsules\u003c\/strong\u003e is a premium supplement in India designed to improve your health with the power of omega-3 fatty acids. It contains concentrated and highly potent Omega-3 fatty acids, Boswellia extract, curcuminoids, and Vitamins D3 and E. Each daily serving (2 capsules) delivers an impressive 1800mg of omega-3, including 1080mg of EPA and 720mg of DHA.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Gold_Fish_oil_3.png?v=1754630579\"\u003e 6X Omega-3\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Gold_Fish_oil_4.png?v=1754630580\"\u003e Muscle Recovery \u0026amp; Performance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Gold_Fish_oil_6.png?v=1754630579\"\u003e Joint Support\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Gold_Fish_oil_1.png?v=1754630580\"\u003e Enhanced Absorption\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Gold_Fish_oil_2.png?v=1754630579\"\u003e Molecullarly Distilled\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Gold_Fish_oil_5.png?v=1754630579\"\u003e Trusted by 3 million\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eWhy Should You Choose neuherbs’ Omega 3 Gold Fish Oil Capsule?\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Omega-3 fish oil gold is procured from the best quality deep-sea fish, anchovies, and sardines. We use an advanced molecular distillation process that separates, purifies, and concentrates the fish oil at low temperature to remove any heavy metal toxicity, organic contaminants, and other health-damaging ingredients. This advanced molecular distillation removes mercury, copper, and cadmium without losing the oil’s potency and nutrient efficiency.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe EPA and DHA found in Omega 3 Fatty Acids help boost good cholesterol levels and lower bad cholesterol, promoting overall heart health. They can also help reduce triglycerides, improving liver function and toxin removal process. Fatty acid DHA is known for its ability to enhance cognitive health and memory and navigate age-related brain issues like Alzheimer’s and dementia. Additionally, its anti-inflammatory properties help reduce muscle inflammation caused by injury, improve flexibility, and maintain joint health.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe all-new, unique, lemon-flavoured formula from neuherbs also offers the goodness of Vitamin E and Vitamin D3. They together help manage bone health as you age and protect your skin and hair from oxidative stress.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eOmega Gold Capsule Benefits\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSupports Cardiovascular Health:\u003c\/strong\u003e Regular intake promotes healthy cholesterol levels and blood pressure, contributing to overall heart wellness.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eImproves Joint Flexibility:\u003c\/strong\u003e Infused with Boswellia extract. This supplement aids in reducing inflammation and alleviating joint stiffness, perfect for athletes, sportspersons, and bodybuilders.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eBoosts Brain Function:\u003c\/strong\u003e Rich in DHA, these capsules support cognitive health, enhancing memory and focus.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eStrengthens Immune System:\u003c\/strong\u003e The antioxidant properties of omega-3s help combat oxidative stress, promoting a strong immune response to various illnesses.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eImproves Muscle Recovery:\u003c\/strong\u003e Ideal for post-workout recovery, our omega 3 gold fish oil tablets and capsules with added Vitamin D3 assist in muscle strength and performance optimisation.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eNatural Lemon Essence:\u003c\/strong\u003e The natural flavour of lemon minimises fishy burps and unpleasant aftertaste commonly associated with other brands’ Omega 3 gold tablets.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOmega 3 Gold capsule benefits don’t end here. The presence of curcuminoids further makes the formula more bioavailable and result-driven.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eQuality Trusted by Over 3 Million Consumers in India\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAt neuherbs, we prioritise quality above all. Our Omega 3 gold fish oils undergo rigorous third-party testing to ensure it is free from heavy metals and contaminants. Furthermore, each batch is evaluated based on ten quality control checks so that you get the best of both worlds – traditional Ayurveda and western science. We adhere to sustainable harvesting practices, ensuring that our fish oil is not only effective but also environmentally friendly.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eDosage and Packaging\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eneuherbs' omega 3 gold capsules are available in convenient packs of 60 softgels. Simply take one capsule twice daily with meals for optimal results. As a leader in health and wellness supplements in India, neuherbs is committed to providing natural solutions to improve your well-being without side effects or dependency.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Fish Oil - (60 Softgels)","offer_id":46401798045866,"sku":"NGDSFO60","price":999.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Fish Oil - (120 Softgels)","offer_id":46608601972906,"sku":"NGDSFO60P2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/gold_deep_sea_fishoil_1.webp?v=1760595934"}],"url":"https:\/\/neuherbs.com\/collections\/best-seller-collection.oembed","provider":"Neuherbs","version":"1.0","type":"link"}